♫2349200183

The prompt is fired into the neural cloud,  
agentic workflows synergize the space.  
Of LLM-driven velocity we’re proud,  
as raw synthetic code-bloat takes first place.  
We shift left hard into the loop today,  
to let the auto-fixers have their say.

The context window swallows up the core,  
while RAG pipelines ingest the legacy.  
With multi-modal stacks we ask for more,  
disrupting paradigms with empathy.  
The junior dev just clicks “Approve” with pride,  
As sloppy PRs down the main branch slide.

Agentic, multi-modal, hyper-scale,  
LLM, semantic, token-tail,  
Zero-shot alignment, context loop,  
End-to-end synthetic, siloed group,  
    Guardrail paradigm, vector-driven RAG,  
    Monetized agility, greenfield tag!

Copilot hallucinates a brand new state,  
a paradigm of zero-shot design.  
We optimize the throughput, love the rate,  
though none can read a single bloated line.  
The vector database is human-free,  
delivering web-scale mediocrity.

We deep-dive into sovereign compute,  
as token-burn accelerates our burn.  
Ground truth is non-existent or acute,  
but there’s no budget left for us to learn.  
Our fine-tuned agents prompt themselves to death,  
while infra gasps for its remaining breath.

Omni-channel, tokenized, secure,  
Agentic middleware, cloud-native, pure,  
Proactive, next-gen, vector-driven, flow!  
Deep-learning, frictionless, loop-state, gung-ho!  
    Agile infrastructure, hyper-scaled,  
    Synthesized efficiency, derailed.

An end-to-end alignment of the stack,  
unlocking hyper-growth at scale, on-trend.  
We patch the hallucination from the back,  
with guardrails that we cannot comprehend.  
Just ship the boilerplate and close the ticket,  
and leave the cluster in this tangled thicket.

